dcterms:description: DBpedia is a large-scale, community-driven project that extracts structured content from the information created in Wikipedia, providing a rich source of linked data.
dcterms:title: DBpedia

dcterms:creator: M. P. Consens
dcterms:description: LinkedMDB is a dataset that provides linked data for movies, actors, and other related entities, allowing for rich querying and exploration of movie-related information.
dcterms:title: LinkedMDB

dcterms:description: The ESBM dataset v1.1 consists of triples related to entities from DBpedia and LinkedMDB, specifically designed for evaluating entity summarization methods.
dcterms:title: ESBM dataset v1.1
